Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Lookan Elementary School in the Municipality of Sapa-Sapa, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Ladja E. Idanan Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 589
An Act Changing the Name of the Lookan Elementary School in the Municipality of Sapa-Sapa, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Ladja E. Idanan Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Lookan Elementary School in the Municipality of Sapa-Sapa, Province of Tawi-Tawi, is hereby changed to Ladja E. Idanan Elementary School.1Ã¢wphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: June 24, 1983
